# Git commits — no Cursor co-author

When creating git commits for this repository:

- Never append `Co-authored-by: Cursor` or any Cursor/agent co-author trailer.
- Commit messages must contain only the human-authored title and body.
- If a hook or tool adds agent attribution, strip it before completing the commit.
